item.description: Hank Lee is a full stack web developer and also software enginner. Currently, he is studying for master of information technology at RMIT university in Australia🇦🇺. He is familiar with Java, Spring Boot, RDBMS and has experiences in HTML/CSS, Javascript, jQuery, Angular. Recently, he is working on ReactJS, Python, Docker and Raspberry Pi in his assessments. In his career, not only does he work as a web developer, but also he has some experiences in pre-sale works.
